{
  "texts": [
    "The total expected number of all datasets types could be more than double [1].",
    "Thus, effective dataset management is critical for decision-making, answering business questions, dataset governance, and gaining a competitive advantage.",
    "In addition, it would help the enterprises to identify trends and spot problems early by making use of the available datasets intelligently.",
    "Abdulaziz Almaslukh and Abdulmajeed Alameer have contributed equally to this work.It has been the traditional wisdom for enterprises to manage their datasets centrally [1][2][3][4][5].",
    "This dataset management paradigm provides better control, reduces redundancy, and simplifies data management."
  ]
}